                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Heard you took the Takehara badge. The meadow talks, you know. Mostly it says well done."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "A badge already. When you beat me here on the blanket, I knew you were headed somewhere."
                        }
                    ],
