                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Picnic day! Every day is picnic day out here. My partners grew up in this meadow - want to meet them?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "You walk like you have somewhere to be. Nobody has somewhere to be on Blossom Path."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "They say Leader Cicada trains standing under the falls. All day. It is why the gym is damp. I have this from a very reliable picnic."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "(one of her partners is asleep under the blanket, holding a grape) Shh. Training day."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Jabari - picnic day",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
